{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"21":"Funerals (Kitab Al-Jana'iz)"},"section_detail":{"21":{"hadithnumber_first":3089,"hadithnumber_last":3241,"arabicnumber_first":3089,"arabicnumber_last":3241}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3186,"arabicnumber":3186,"text":"حدثنا ابو كامل، حدثنا ابو عوانة، عن ابي بشر، حدثني نفر، من اهل البصرة عن ابي برزة الاسلمي، ان رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم لم يصل على ماعز بن مالك ولم ينه عن الصلاة عليه","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":98}}]}